Data_Year: The year the data was collected, providing a timeline for analysis.
Battery_Lifespan_Years: Average lifespan of EV batteries in years, reflecting the durability and effectiveness of the batteries.
AI_Enhanced_Management: Indicates whether AI-enhanced battery management was used during data collection, relevant for assessing technological impact.
Data_Collection_Quarter: The quarter in which the data was collected (e.g., Q1, Q2, Q3, Q4), providing more granular time reference.
Region: The geographical region where the data was collected, important for regional compliance and market analysis.
